      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月三日　朝",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、お誕生日おめでとうございます！\nお祝いを込めて、本日は私自らさくらに――",
      "startTime": 6.6892934065,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7610.706593500001,
          "startTime": 14.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "エレガントでセレブリティなアイドルの\nモーニングルーティンを伝授して差し上げますわ！",
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "まずはこちら！　私が愛用しているメーカーの美容液！\n奮発してちょっとお高いのをプレゼントいたしますわ！",
      "startTime": 23.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　ありがとう！　これって最近、kanaさんも\nメディアでオススメしてたあの有名な……！",
      "startTime": 32.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こほんっ！　わ、私の方が先に使ってますのよ！\nこの美容液をたっぷり手に……",
      "startTime": 41.8333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "おお！　お高い美容液を惜しみなく……！\nさすがはセレブリティ！",
      "startTime": 49.1333325704,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.000762900001,
          "startTime": 56.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9100.000762900003,
          "startTime": 58.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、たっぷり手に取りたい気持ちをぐっと堪え\n気持ち少なめに出してお顔にぽん！",
      "startTime": 55.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "セレブとは物の価値を理解している者！\n節約こそが真のセレブ道なのですわ！",
      "startTime": 63.5044999805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、勉強になります！\n節約、節約！　ナイスセレブリティ！",
      "startTime": 70.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "次なるモーニングルーティンは……朝からヨガ！\n八曲がりのポーズ！　ふぎっ！　ふぎぎぎぎ……っ！",
      "startTime": 79.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ルーティンと呼ぶにはあまりに不慣れな動き……！\n関節が変な方向に曲がってるようで曲がってない！？",
      "startTime": 88.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "セ……セレブとは苦手なことにも果敢に挑む者！\n挑戦こそが真のセレブ道なのですわ！",
      "startTime": 99.5999994913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだね……！\n挑戦、挑戦！　ナイスセレブリティ！",
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "次なるモーニングルーティンは……\n美容にいい食事！　アサイーボウル！",
      "startTime": 112.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "――の、つもりだったのですが\n昨晩試食したらあんまりお口に合いませんでしたの",
      "startTime": 120.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "なので、遙子さんが作った朝食をいただきましょう\n朝は美味しいものを食べないと元気出ませんもの！",
      "startTime": 130.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "これは紛れもなくルーティン！　あれれ、でもこれって\nもう遙子さんからのプレゼントでは！？",
      "startTime": 140.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "セレブとは日常のありがたみを知る者！\n遙子メシなくして真のセレブ道などありえませんわ！",
      "startTime": 147.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだね……！　ありがたや遙子さん……！\n日常、日常！　ナイスセレブリティ！",
      "startTime": 156.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、最後のモーニングルーティン！\nセレブらしい装いを整えたら完成ですわ！",
      "startTime": 164.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "今日は特別に！　私のセレブなクリエイティビティを\n爆発させ、さくらのヘアセットをしてあげますわ！",
      "startTime": 173.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "おおおおお～～～！！\nナイスセレブリティ！！！！",
      "startTime": 184.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "さあ！　朝のレッスンに向かいますわよ！\nセレブな高笑いをあげながら！　小粋なスキップで！",
      "startTime": 190.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.33333339998,
          "startTime": 197.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "お～～～～ほっほっほっほ！！",
      "startTime": 195.1666636152,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}